main event: General (ret.) reported sighting of UFOs on 17 May 1954 in Sweden.
interesting points: The sighting was evaluated as probably meteors.
The report was received by the Air Technical Intelligence Center (ATIC) on 27 July 1954.
The report was assigned Project No. DEACT 2B.S.0.55.
The document appears to be a page from a Project Blue Book record, which was a project by the United States Air Force to investigate unidentified flying objects (UFOs).
There is no photograph present in the image.
